<span class="displaytext">des moines, ia -- on friday, november 9, senator (candidate full) will host a roundtable discussion with local women about his plan to reclaim the american dream. (candidate last)'s plan, unveiled this week in bettendorf, includes guaranteeing paid sick days, expanding the family and medical leave act (fmla), supporting paid fmla, and doubling funding for after-school programs. <p>(candidate last)'s wide-sweeping legislation to reclaim the american dream will address the economic challenges women face. to read more about his plan, click <a href="http://my.(candidate full).com/page/-/hqpress/110707%20final%20national%20fact%20sheet%20american%20dream.pdf">here</a>.</p></span>



